  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Pastel_Shaders/BH_Pastel_Shaders_Header.png\" alt=\"Pastel Shader's logo\" width=\"1024\" height=\"324\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://lunapixel.studio/discord\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/790272037578473512?label=Discord&amp;color=ffe8e9&amp;labelColor=ffced2&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=blue\" width=\"205\" height=\"26\" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/SUPPORTS-IRIS,%20OCULUS,%20OPTIFINE%20|%201.7%20to%201.20-ffe8e9?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=Modrinth&amp;labelColor=ffced2\" width=\"385\" height=\"28\" />&nbsp; &nbsp; <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/elocindev\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/ElocinDev-SUPPORT%20ME-ffe8e9?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=Ko-Fi&amp;labelColor=ffced2\" width=\"212\" height=\"27\" /></a></em><em>&nbsp;</em>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/ELOCIN\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Pastel_Shaders/BH_Pastel_Shaders_Promo.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1018\" height=\"151\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Pastel Shaders is a stylized aesthetic shaderpack that features multiple color presets</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/977751810922131456/1066006073456197652/presets-transparent.gif\" alt=\"All three presets featured in Pastel Shaders\" width=\"1200\" height=\"608\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/977751810922131456/1066223943956041748/highperformance.png\" alt=\"Pastel is a high performance shader.\" width=\"1120\" height=\"567\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>🎨 Multiple color presets</strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">From pinkish, to blueish and yellowish pastel color palletes to choose from!&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>🌌 Chill atmosphere</strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;Near vanilla experience with clear, starry skies. Beautiful sunsets and sunrises.</p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>✏️ High customization</strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;For both new and advanced users, customization is easy and almost unlimited!</p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>⚙️ User-friendly settings menu</strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;Too much settings overwhelms you? Pastel has quick settings similar to most</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">modern games.</p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>💻&nbsp;Runs on most modern PC's</strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;Optimized even for modern low end GPUs and even integrated graphics!</p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>☁️ Sibling of the <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/shader/insanity-shader\">Insanity Shaderpack</a></strong></span>\n<p>Pastel is the opposite version of Insanity, which is Based on BSL Shaders &hearts;!</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
